title: RLadiesData
text: RLadies data pkg dataset package RLadies meetups, datasets specific RLadies use. datasets cleaned tidy educational learning reasons. can install package load library can also select dataset want work . Available datasets : CountryCapitals Happiness PhillyFarmersMarket RLadiesChapters

title: RLadiesData — CountryCapitals
text: tibble 243 rows 7 variables: CountryName chr name Country CapitalName chr name capital city Country CapitalLatitude num latitude coordinate city country. CapitalLongitude num longitude coordinate city country. CountryCode chr abbreviation country code ContinentName chr name Continent Country city

title: RLadiesData — Happiness
text: World Happiness Report (2016) ranks 156 countries happiness levels.

title: RLadiesData — Happiness
text: tibble 157 rows 14 variables: Country chr name Country Region chr geographical region Country Happiness.Rank int value happiness. 6 factors calculated score : GDP, social suppot, health life expectancy, life choices freedom, generosity perceptions corruption. lower value happier ranking. Happiness.Score num statistical average happiness scores. Lower.Confidence.Interval num lower confidence interval happiness score. Upper.Confidence.Interval num upper confidence interval happiness score. Economy.GDP.per.capita num Gross Domestic Gross country terms Purchasing Power Parity used World Development Indicators (WDI) Family num Average family happiness ranking Health.Life.Expectancy num average health life expectancy scores. Freedom num average score personal freedoms Trust.Government.Corruption num average score level personal trust government Dystopia.Residual num statistical residual affect dystopian views life.
